description:
This is a 16 minute workout called '15 Min High Intensity Elliptical Cardio Climber HIIT' from the channel Sunny Health & Fitness.
The workout falls under Cardio/Elliptical and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.
